sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant S as Express_API
  participant D as MongoDB
  C->>S: POST /api/auth/login
  S->>D: User.findOne email
  D-->>S: user document
  S->>S: bcrypt compare + JWT
  S-->>C: token + user
  C->>S: GET /api/posts Bearer JWT
  S->>S: authenticateToken
  S->>D: Post.find
  S-->>C: posts JSON
